      "id": "q-resource-hints",
      "navLabel": "资源提示",
      "question": "dns-prefetch、preconnect、preload、prefetch 怎么选？",
      "questionNote": "资源提示（Resource Hints）按「解析 → 建连 → 本页关键 → 下页预取」递进使用。",
      "answer": [
        [
          {
            "type": "code",
            "value": "dns-prefetch"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "value": "：只做域名解析（DNS）。"
          }
        ],
        [
          {
            "type": "code",
            "value": "preconnect"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "value": "：解析 + TCP + 传输层安全（TLS），适合马上要用第三方接口或 CDN。"
          }
        ],
        [
          {
            "type": "code",
            "value": "preload"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "value": "：高优先级拉本页 LCP 图、关键 CSS；"
          },
          {
            "type": "code",
            "value": "as"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "value": " 类型须与真实请求一致，滥用会抢带宽。"
          }
        ],
        [
          {
            "type": "code",
            "value": "prefetch"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "value": "：空闲预取下一路由 chunk。可与网络安全章 DNS/TLS 优化一起答。"
          }
        ],
        [
          {
            "type": "strong",
            "value": "示例："
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "value": "常用 hint 对照。"
          }
        ],
        [
          {
            "type": "code",
            "value": "<link rel=\"dns-prefetch\" href=\"//cdn.example.com\">\n<link rel=\"preconnect\" href=\"https://api.example.com\" crossorigin>\n<link rel=\"preload\" href=\"/font.woff2\" as=\"font\" crossorigin>\n<link rel=\"prefetch\" href=\"/next-page.js\">"
          }
        ]
      ]
    },
